								<!-- bodycontent -->
				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="dablink">"Copyrighting" redirects here. For the use of words to promote or advertise something, see <a href="Copywriting" title="Copywriting">Copywriting</a>.</div>
<div class="dablink"><span class="plainlinks selfreference">"Copyrights" redirects here. For Wikipedia policy about copyright issues, see <a href="Wikipedia_Copyrights" title="Wikipedia:Copyrights">Wikipedia:Copyrights</a>.</span></div>
