<tr>
<td style="text-align:right;font-size:115%;">
<div class="noprint plainlinks hlist navbar mini" style="">
<ul>
<li class="nv-view"><a href="Template_Intellectual_property" title="Template:Intellectual property"><span title="View this template" style="">v</span></a></li>
<li class="nv-talk"><a href="Template_talk_Intellectual_property" title="Template talk:Intellectual property"><span title="Discuss this template" style="">t</span></a></li>
