<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=Copyright&action=edit&section=22.php.html" title="Edit section: Treaties and international agreements">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Treaties_and_international_agreements">Treaties and international agreements</span></h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="Berne_Convention_for_the_Protection_of_Literary_and_Artistic_Works" title="Berne Convention for the Protection of Literary and Artistic Works">Berne Convention for the Protection of Literary and Artistic Works</a> of 1886</li>
<li><a href="Rome_Convention_for_the_Protection_of_Performers,_Producers_of_Phonograms_and_Broadcasting_Organisations" title="Rome Convention for the Protection of Performers, Producers of Phonograms and Broadcasting Organisations">Rome Convention for the Protection of Performers, Producers of Phonograms and Broadcasting Organisations</a> of 1961</li>
<li><a href="Universal_Copyright_Convention" title="Universal Copyright Convention">Universal Copyright Convention</a> of 1952</li>
<li><a href="World_Intellectual_Property_Organization_Copyright_Treaty" title="World Intellectual Property Organization Copyright Treaty">World Intellectual Property Organization Copyright Treaty</a> of 1996</li>
<li><a href="WIPO_Performances_and_Phonograms_Treaty" title="WIPO Performances and Phonograms Treaty">WIPO Performances and Phonograms Treaty</a> of 1996</li>
